ndustrial scale.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aEconomicsxPolitical EconomicsxHistory of Economics. 0aHistoryxHistorical PeriodsxContemporary HistoryxContemporary History until 1945. 0aHistoryxTopics in HistoryxEconomic conditions. 4aIndustriegeschichte. 4aRohstoffe. 4aWirtschaftsgeschichte. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Germany.2bisacsh  aIndustrial history.  aeconomic history.  araw materials.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2014z9783110370225oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831103972530 cprintz978311035127940uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978311035138540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110351385423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110351385/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2014  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014